---

<div
  class="lg:col-span-8 bg-surface-container neobrutal-border neobrutal-shadow rounded-lg p-6 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-start gap-6 min-h-[360px]"
>
  <!-- Version badge -->
  <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-fixed border-2 border-black px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs rounded">
    SYS.ARCH_v2.4
  </div>

  <!-- Title + bio -->
  <div class="z-10 mt-6">
    <h1 class="font-mono text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface uppercase leading-tight mb-4">
      SYSTEMS <span class="text-primary">RESEARCHER</span>
      <br />&amp; ARCHITECT
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mt-6 border-l-2 border-primary pl-4 leading-relaxed">
      Designing robust distributed systems, engineering compilers, and
      contributing to the architectural integrity of decentralized protocols.
      Polkadot Fellowship Core Contributor.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- CTAs -->
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 z-10">
    <a
      href="#contact"
      id="cta-contact"
      class="bg-primary text-on-primary-fixed neobrutal-border neobrutal-shadow px-6 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase rounded transition-all hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_#000] active:translate-x-1 active:translate-y-1 active:shadow-none inline-flex items-center gap-2"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">terminal</span>
      INITIALIZE_CONTACT
    </a>
    <a
      href="/cv"
      class="bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface neobrutal-border neobrutal-shadow px-6 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase rounded transition-all hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_#000] active:translate-x-1 active:translate-y-1 active:shadow-none inline-flex items-center gap-2"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">download</span>
      PULL_CV.PDF
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative overlay -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</div>

